  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p874669/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/10/26/b81c5d6fd6cca19c421a3cf9144d36e0.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">What Is The Most Unusual <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Password\" target=\"_blank\">Password</a> You Have Ever Seen?</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">你见过的最奇葩的密码是什么？</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">获得16.6k 好评的回答@Omar Patel</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Most people tend not to believe me, but this was the password for my old laptop (it took me about 4.73 hours of just staring at it to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/memorize\" target=\"_blank\">memorize</a> this)大部分人可能不太相信我，但是这确实是我旧笔记本电脑的密码（我花了差不多4,73小时死死盯着它去记住它）</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">caledfwlch13214874890703.pdx97bballcclbj23&hellip;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&hellip;SOS</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">获得138好评的回答@Mishall Rajkumar</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">It&rsquo;s my brother&rsquo;s.这是我哥的。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">His facebook password is INCORRECT. Actually he is very bad at remembering passwords. So, if he types his password wrongly, the computer says &ldquo;Your password is Incorrect&rdquo;. And then he remembers it. Quite crazy isn&rsquo;t it?他的脸书密码是&ldquo;不正确的&rdquo;。实际上他记性非常差，记不住密码。因此，如果他输入密码错误，电脑就会显示&ldquo;您的密码是不正确的。&rdquo;于是乎他就记住了。相当奇葩，有木有？</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">获得847好评的回答@Avadhesh Khanna</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Well, It&rsquo;s not unusual password, but unusual <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/trick\" target=\"_blank\">trick</a>, my brother used. Let&rsquo;s say his mobile number is 9512346978.&nbsp; 这不是一组奇特密码，但密码的诀窍却很奇特，是我哥曾用过的。他的手机号码是 9512346978.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">He typed password on computer <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/numpad\" target=\"_blank\">numpad</a> while imagining as mobile <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/keypad\" target=\"_blank\">keypad</a>.他使用电脑的小键盘输入密码，输的时候想象那是手机的拨号键盘。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1 becomes 71变成了7</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">2 becomes 8 2变成了8</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">3 becomes 9&hellip;and so on. 3变成了9... 等等</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">His password becomes:于是乎，他的密码变成：</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">[/cn</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">]</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">3578946312</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">获得494好评的回答@Dan Holliday</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">If very long passwords are allowed, I just use a sentence. One of my older ones was:如果允许使用超长密码的话，我会使用长句。曾用过的一个密码是：</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">I.am.the.very.model.of.a.modern.Major-General!</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">我。是。现。代。少。将。的。楷。模！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">It&rsquo;s not 100%&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unhackable\" target=\"_blank\">unhackable</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">. It has the advantage of being&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/singable\" target=\"_blank\">singable</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;and practically unforgettable for me.这个也不是百分之百无法破解。但它的好处是朗朗上口，而且对我来说基本不会忘记。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.8em;\">声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p874669/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p874669\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p749886/\">英语四级听力：超准！听力5大原则</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p870694/\">你真的不用以此为耻，这9件事再正常不过了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p856860/\">快收下这50个表达心情的常用词 别蓝瘦香菇了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p871671/\">慢半拍的老外终于开始集体吐槽《爵迹》了……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p857774/\">《生活大爆炸》追剧笔记S10E3：这瓶我请</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p872844/\">手指长短见天赋：你是运动达人还是记忆天才</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p844721/\">双语美文：桥下那位流浪汉教会了我什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p874583/\">《爸爸去哪儿4》：去哪找阿拉蕾这么萌的娃啊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p857798/\">今秋最值得学的10门英语课程</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p871723/\">成语翻译：白头偕老&百发百中</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a 